# 🔹 Data Types

Python supports different types of data.

| Data Type | Example    |
| --------- | ---------- |
| String    | `"Python"` |
| Integer   | `10`       |
| Float     | `8.5`      |
| Boolean   | `True`     |
| Complex   | `4 + 5j`   |

### Learned:

* Understanding different data types
* Using `type()` function
* Difference between numeric and text values

